\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on the past, McIlroy admitted in 2016 that he found the debate over which nation he would represent at the Olympics frustrating, expressing 'resentment' over the discourse.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 810}, {\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"the debate\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"which nation\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"resentment\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"the discourse\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Golf returned to the Games in Rio de Janeiro that year for the first time since 1904, but McIlroy did not participate.\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1002, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9999999991655386, \"rank\": 8.343716720071711e-10, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Golf\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After years of speculation, he finally chose to represent Team Ireland at the Tokyo Olympics three years ago.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1150, \"end\": 1162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6962942594060408e-16, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"speculation\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1118}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on the intense scrutiny over his national allegiance in an interview with theSunday Independentfive years earlier, he expressed his frustration: \\\"All of a sudden it put me in a position where I had to question who I am.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the intense scrutiny\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"his national allegiance\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"theSunday\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"his frustration\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1356}, {\"ngram\": \"a position\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Who am I?\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Where am I from?\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Where do my loyalties lie?\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my loyalties\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Who am I going to play for?\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Who do I not want to (upset) the most?\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I started to resent it.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I do.\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I resent the Olympic Games because of the position it put me in.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"the position\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's my feelings toward it.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1684, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my feelings\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And whether that's right or wrong, that's how I feel.\\\"\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also shared a personal revelation about his potential reaction to national anthems: \\\"I said, 'Justin, if I had been on the podium (listening) to the Irish national anthem as that flag went up, or the British national anthem as that flag went up, I would have felt uncomfortable either way',\\\" he confessed.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 2049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1893, \"end\": 1914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amhr\\u00e1n_na_bhFiann\", \"score\": 0.9999999960980404, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irish national anthem\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amhr\\u00e1n_na_bhFiann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amhr\\u00e1n_na_bhFiann\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a personal revelation\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"his potential reaction\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1806}, {\"ngram\": \"national anthems\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1873}, {\"ngram\": \"that flag\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"that flag\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 1980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know the words to either anthem.\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2092, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the words\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"either anthem\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not feel a connection to either flag.\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a connection\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2119}, {\"ngram\": \"either flag\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not want it to be about flags.\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"flags\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have tried to stay away from that.\\\"\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the end, his decision was influenced by his past experiences representing a nation at junior and amateur levels, as he explained the motivation behind his choice: \\\"As I said, previously, once I left trying not to upset anyone aside, then it was actually a pretty easy decision.\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2491, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"his decision\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"his past experiences\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"a nation\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"junior and amateur levels\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2325}, {\"ngram\": \"the motivation\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2357}, {\"ngram\": \"his choice\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2375}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"a pretty easy decision\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your sign-up\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"content\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2539}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2594}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2627}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"3rd pa